    - Name: tooltip
      Entry: 1
      Data: "Optional reference to the scene's AvatarScalingSettings UdonBehaviour
        (the SDK sample, or any compatible UB exposing `minimumHeight` / `maximumHeight`
        floats). If wired, the script reads those values on station entry and uses
        them as the clamp bounds \u2014 single source of truth, no duplication. If
        null, falls back to minScale/maxScale below (relative to player's entry eye
        height)."
